    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based,<strong> hob-safe</strong> <strong>oven-proof casserole dish</strong> with a matching lid with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Chop the <strong>tomatoes </strong>into wedges</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
