      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> meat-free mince</strong> (remove the paper if required!) to the dish with the<strong> dried oregano, bay leaf<span class=\"text-danger\">[ves]</span></strong> and <strong>baharat</strong> and<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>cook for 2-3 min, breaking the mince into rough, large chunks until very lightly browned all over</p>",
