    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, deseed the <strong>sweet pointed pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>and slice into rings</p><p>Add the <strong>pepper rings</strong> and<strong> tomato wedges </strong>to the dish, season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give everything a good stir</p><p>Put the dish in the oven, covered, for an initial 15 min</p>",
